cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with object detection and classification using unsupervised multi-instance object discovery algorithms and convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves algorithms for object identification and classification, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves multimedia techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
